        s4body: "Payment for individual sessions is required in full before the scheduled session, by bank transfer or another online payment method provided by Empirica. For packages, workshops or group events, a deposit may be required to secure a place, with remaining payment details communicated before booking confirmation. Deposit amounts and payment schedules will be clearly explained before purchase.",
