        s5body: "Clients may request to reschedule a session by providing at least 24 hours' notice. Where sufficient notice is provided, Empirica will make reasonable efforts to offer an alternative appointment. Cancellations made with less than 24 hours' notice, or failure to attend a scheduled session, may result in the full session fee being retained. Exceptional circumstances may be considered at Empirica's discretion on a case-by-case basis.",
        s6title: "Online Sessions",
        s6body: "For online sessions, clients are responsible for ensuring a suitable private space, a stable internet connection, and appropriate technology. Empirica is not responsible for interruptions caused by technical issues outside of its control.",
        s7title: "In-Person Sessions",
        s7body: "In-person sessions may take place at selected professional venues or agreed locations across the UK. Venue details will be provided after booking confirmation. Empirica does not operate from a private residential address. Clients are responsible for arriving at the agreed location on time.",
        s8title: "Workshops & Group Sessions",
        s8body: "For workshops and group events, spaces may be limited, booking confirmation is required, and specific event terms may apply. Participants are expected to respect the privacy, safety and wellbeing of other attendees.",
