        s6body: "Akashic Records and Intuitive Guidance sessions are offered as reflective and spiritual practices. Any insights, messages or interpretations shared during a session are personal perspectives intended for reflection and exploration. Clients are encouraged to use their own judgement and intuition, and Empirica does not claim to predict the future or provide certainty about future events.",
