        s8body: "Empirica is committed to creating a safe, respectful and confidential environment. Sessions are approached with compassion, discretion, respect and professional boundaries. Confidentiality may be limited where there is a legal requirement or serious concern regarding safety.",
        s9title: "Suitability of Services",
        s9body: "Empirica reserves the right to recommend that a client seeks additional or alternative professional support where appropriate, including situations where specialist medical, psychological or other professional assistance would be more suitable.",
        s10title: "Client Agreement",
        s10body: "By booking a session with Empirica, clients acknowledge that they understand the nature of the services offered, that sessions are complementary wellbeing practices, that they remain responsible for their own choices and wellbeing, and that no specific outcomes are guaranteed.",
